# QuoteFlow - core conventions

Read `AGENTS.md` for the full map. Skills: `.agents/skills/quoteflow/SKILL.md`, `.agents/skills/gluestack-ui-v4/SKILL.md`.

## Stack

- **pnpm** + **Turbo** monorepo
- **Next.js 16** (`apps/web`) with **webpack** (not Turbopack)
- **@repo/ui** - Gluestack UI v4 + NativeWind + Tailwind 3.4

## Commands

```bash
pnpm install && pnpm dev:web
pnpm build && pnpm lint && pnpm typecheck
pnpm ui:add <name>          # Gluestack component → packages/ui
pnpm skills:install         # Refresh .agents/skills/gluestack-ui-v4
```

## Where to edit

| Do | Don't |
|----|-------|
| Screens in `packages/ui/src/screens/` | Business UI in `apps/web/` |
| Routes in `apps/web/app/**/page.tsx` | Duplicate components in apps/web |
| Store hooks in `@repo/ui` | TanStack Query hooks + `ApiQueryProvider` in `packages/api/` |
| Theme in `globals.css` + `config.ts` | Hardcoded hex colors |

## Principles

- Minimal, focused diffs; match existing naming and patterns
- Avoid `any` / `unknown` in TypeScript
- No git commits or PRs unless the user asks
- Demo login: `admin@example.com` / `password123`
